content.rendered:
Directed by Rohit Shetty.

Written by Farhad Samji. Sajid.

Cast Shah Rukh Khan(Raj / Kaali). Kajol(Meera Malik). Varun Dhawan(Veer). Kriti Sanon(Ishita Malik). Varun Sharma(Sidhu). Boman Irani(King). Johny Lever(Money Bhai (as Johnny Lever)). Mukesh Tiwari(Shakti). Pankaj Tripathi(Anwar (as Pankaj Tripathy)). Sanjay Mishra(Oscar Bhai). Chetna Pande(Jenny). Vinod Khanna(Randheer Bakshi). Kabir Bedi(Dev Malik).Murli Sharma. Ahmad Shaikh(Tawde). Mitansh Lulla(Young Veer). Stuti Dixit(Young Ishita) . Naushaad Abbas(King’s Henchman). Kamal Adib(Uncle Joe). Mukesh Agrohari(Anthony).Shawar Ali. Peter Fernandes(King’s Driver). Pradeep Kabra(Joshua). Jahangir Khan(Patrick). Krishna Kotian(Peter). Yogesh Lakhani(Customer At The Cafe). Vladimir Mihaylov(Bulgarian Goon (as Vladimir Mihailov)). Avinash Ojha(Pintoo).Chetan Pandit. Umair Patel(Musical Artist (archive sound)).Samrat Raichand. Rajlaxmi(Meera’s Maid). Sunil Rodrigues(Robert). Sangar(Divan). Sujit Sen(Doctor). Nawab Shah(Raghav). Vineet Sharma(Kaali’s Man).Sharad Vittal Shetty. Abhinay Raj Singh(Chotuuu). Samiran Singh(Singer)

Language Hindi.

Producers Elisabeth Agnarsdottir. Bunty Arora. Sadashiv Athule. Mangesh Bhalerao. George Cameron. KS Jairam. Gauri Khan. Sameer Khan. Karim Morani. Natarajan Ramji. Anil Sable. Rohit Shetty. Leti Singh. Iliya Sotirov.

Production Redchillies.VFX. Rohit Shetty Productions.
